title: Goblin (disambiguation)

properties.name: description
properties.value: Several types of Goblin can be found throughout Gielinor:

content:
Several types of Goblin can be found throughout Gielinor:

  • Regular Goblins
  • Goblins found in Goblin Village
  • Goblins found in the Vault of War inside the Stronghold of Security
  • Goblins found in the God Wars Dungeons
  • Goblin students found in the Surprise Exam random event
  • A Goblin guard, found in the Observatory Dungeon

Some goblins used to exist in the game, but have since been removed:

  • 2019 Halloween goblins
  • 2020 Christmas goblins
  • Old Goblin Village goblins

Related NPCs and monsters are:

  • Cave goblin
  • Hobgoblin
  • Reanimated goblin
  • Revenant goblin
  • Revenant hobgoblin
  • The Angry goblin from A Soul's Bane
  • Goblin fish

Locations inhabited by Goblins are:

  • Goblin Village
  • Goblin Cave
  • The Goblin settlement near the Observatory

Related music tracks:

  • Goblin Village
  • Cave of the Goblins

Related content:

  • Goblin Diplomacy
  • Goblin mail
  • Goblin book
  • Goblin mask
  • Goblin bow
  • Goblin salute
  • Ensouled goblin head
  • Goblin skull
  • The Cursed goblin weapons:
    • Cursed goblin bow
    • Cursed goblin hammer
    • Cursed goblin staff


 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.
If an internal link led you to this disambiguation page, you may wish to change the link to point directly to the intended article.
